&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Follow the direction of warehouse management to effectively organize inventory in bulk storage areas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Regularly review and update picking locations, bins, and labels to update inventory and align with our warehouse management system&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
